race.comment: PEERLESS LAD (3) spiked his figures winning this grade/trip and then found 1300m too short last time. Maps well and tumbles in weight with a claimer engaged. He can bounce back. CARAT TIME (1) is racing well and is close to a win. Best figures measure up and he placed his only go at a mile. Sure to run well. STYLE AND GRACE (2) missed a whisker this grade/trip and then led again back to 1300m and was overrun in the latter stages as favourite. She's going to be much more prominent back up to the 1600m and she also has claims. MIGHTY ZOU (7) peaks for this and will be around the mark in this company.
